#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:diy_workshops.homepage
msgid ""
"<br/> Want to know more about our DIY workshops? Whether you're curious "
"about dates, materials, or private group options, feel free to get in "
"touch;&amp;nbsp;we're happy to guide you! Reach us via email, phone, or our "
"contact form and we'll respond within 24 hours.&amp;nbsp;<br/>"
